<p class="">The House will remember that I only referred to the right hon. Gentleman the Secretary of State for War, saying that it would only be fair to allow him to make a statement considering that the other persons concerned had already been allowed to make a statement to the House. I must leave it to the right hon. Gentleman.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
