            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-612d7e87-7356-4a56-8c27-89cc82244c4a">
                Major Macnamara
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-612d7e87-7356-4a56-8c27-89cc82244c4a" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
